description.plain: Adam Tensta (born Adam Momodou Eriksson Taal 1 August 1983 in Tensta, Stockholm, Sweden), is a Swedish rapper of part Gambian descent. His debut album It’s a Tensta Thing was a Swedish chart topper, and was awarded the 2008 Grammis for best Dance/Hip Hop/Soul album. His song “My Cool” was featured in NBA 2k10. Adam is signed to Swedish imprint RMH, Respect My Hustle.

body.plain: Adam Tensta (born Adam Momodou Eriksson Taal 1 August 1983 in Tensta, Stockholm, Sweden), is a Swedish rapper of part Gambian descent. Adam is signed to Swedish imprint RMH, Respect My Hustle.
